annotationA: Autophagy-related 7 is an E1-type ligase for the autophagic ubiquitin-like proteins Atg8a and Atg12. Its roles include autophagosome formation, maintaining neuromuscular function and normal lifespan
annotationB: CG7220, isoform B; Ubiquitin-protein transferase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: proteolysis; protein monoubiquitination; Belongs to the ubiquitin-conjugating enzyme family
